sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Scripts as scripts/
    participant Data as data.py
    participant Models as models.py
    participant CV as cross_validation.py
    participant Env as environment_validation.py
    participant Features as feature_engineering.py
    participant Select as feature_selection.py
    participant Uncertainty as uncertainty.py
    participant Reliability as reliability_scoreboard.py
    participant Outputs as results + figures + reports

    User->>Scripts: run generate_all_results.py
    Scripts->>Data: curate raw QSAR dataset
    Data-->>Outputs: curated CSV + metadata + dataset report

    Scripts->>Models: run baseline classifiers
    Models->>Data: load/split descriptor dataset
    Models-->>Outputs: baseline metrics + report

    Scripts->>Models: run feedforward neural network baseline
    Models->>Data: load/split descriptor dataset
    Models-->>Outputs: neural baseline metrics + FNN finding report

    Scripts->>Env: run proxy cross-environment validation
    Env->>Data: load descriptor dataset
    Env-->>Outputs: cross-environment tables + figures + report

    Scripts->>CV: run stratified cross-validation
    CV->>Data: load descriptor dataset
    CV-->>Outputs: fold diagnostics + model metrics

    Scripts->>Features: compare baseline vs proxy chemistry features
    Features->>Data: load and standardize descriptors
    Features->>CV: evaluate feature sets
    Features-->>Outputs: feature-engineering tables + figure + summary

    Scripts->>Select: rank features and evaluate selected sets
    Select->>Features: build enhanced feature matrix
    Select->>CV: evaluate selected feature sets
    Select->>Env: test selected sets under environment shift
    Select-->>Outputs: feature rankings + selection tables + figures

    Scripts->>Uncertainty: evaluate calibration and uncertainty
    Uncertainty->>Select: reuse selected feature sets
    Uncertainty->>Env: evaluate cross-environment reliability
    Uncertainty-->>Outputs: uncertainty metrics + prediction-level outputs + figures

    Scripts->>Reliability: build final reliability scoreboard
    Reliability->>Uncertainty: reuse uncertainty outputs
    Reliability-->>Outputs: final scoreboard + model reliability report + model-selection figures
